# Conventional Commit Message Template
# Usar el formato: type(scope): description
#
# Tipos válidos / Valid types:
# feat:     Nueva característica / New feature
# fix:      Corrección de bug / Bug fix
# docs:     Documentación / Documentation
# style:    Cambios de formato / Formatting changes
# refactor: Refactorización / Refactoring
# test:     Tests / Testing
# chore:    Tareas de mantenimiento / Maintenance tasks
# perf:     Mejoras de rendimiento / Performance improvements
# ci:       Integración continua / Continuous integration
# build:    Sistema de build / Build system
# revert:   Revertir cambios / Revert changes
#
# Ejemplos / Examples:
# feat(auth): add JWT authentication system
# fix(tenant): resolve database connection issue
# docs(readme): update installation instructions
# style(lint): fix code formatting issues
# refactor(user): simplify user type validation
# test(tenant): add unit tests for tenant creation
# chore(deps): update Laravel to v12
#
# Formato completo / Full format:
# type(scope): short description (max 50 chars)
#
# Longer description explaining what and why (wrap at 72 chars)
#
# Fixes #123
# Closes #456
# Co-authored-by: Name <email@example.com>

